<h1>Post</h1>

<p>Nothing says Christmas spirit quite like the look of complete, abject terror on your child's face as they sit on that &quot;big mean red guys&quot; lap:</p>
<img src="http://www.camdenfamily.com/morpheus/blog/images/xmas2003.jpg">
<p>Number one is <i>slowly</i> getting over his fear - he was able to ask Santa for a telescope and legos this year. Number two and number three are, well, not quite ready yet for the whole Santa thing.</p>
<p>By the way, I resized this picture using a handy <a href="http://www.microsoft.com/windowsxp/pro/downloads/powertoys.asp">Power Toy</a> from Microsoft called Image Resizer. I love being able to quickly resize an image directly from Explorer.</p>
